data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLERS ASK ABOUT BUYER INCENTIVES........
Charming Family Home in Coveted Anniston Elementary and Bayou View Junior High School District!

Welcome to Your Perfect Family Haven! This fantastic 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in the highly sought-after Anniston Elementary and Bayou View Junior High School District, providing an exceptional education for your children. With its prime location, you'll be just a stone's throw away from pristine beaches, convenient shopping, and all the amenities you desire.

Coastal Convenience at Your Doorstep: Imagine living within minutes of stunning beaches, where weekends can be filled with sun-soaked adventures and relaxing ocean breezes. Embrace the coastal lifestyle you've been dreaming of!

Retail Therapy and More: Enjoy easy access to a variety of shopping destinations, from charming boutiques to modern malls, ensuring your retail needs are always met. Indulge in a shopping spree or find unique treasures to decorate your new home.

No Flood Insurance Required: Rest easy knowing that your investment is secure, as this lovely abode is situated in a no-flood-insurance-required zone, providing you with peace of mind and potential cost savings.

A Spacious and Inviting Retreat: Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open floor plan, a true masterpiece for family living. The living area boasts a soaring vaulted ceiling adorned with exquisite exposed beams, perfectly complementing the timeless brick fireplace, creating an ambiance that's both cozy and sophisticated.

Modern Upgrades: The heart of the home, the kitchen, was expertly updated in 2018 with sleek cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops. Whether you're preparing a quick weekday meal or hosting a grand feast, this kitchen is designed to cater to your culinary aspirations.

Elegance Meets Functionality: Gorgeous hardwood flooring flows throughout the home, lending a touch of classic elegance and easy maintenance. The fenced backyard offers a safe haven for outdoor play and relaxation, while an attractive storage shed provides practicality without compromising on style.

Mark Your Calendar: Please note that the property is currently occupied, and appointments are required to ensure a smooth and respectful showing experience for all parties involved.

Claim Your Slice of Paradise: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a superb family home in a top-tier school district, close to beaches, shopping, and all the amenities you adore. Contact us today to schedule your appointment and make this home yours!

Note: All information provided is deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Prospective buyers are advised to verify all details independently.
